        "name": "Test samples acceptance criteria",
        "description": "N=11 production-representative constructs from the same manufacturing lot, tested across two independent laboratories. Achieved Gradation 3: sample-to-sample variability characterized and reported."
      },
      "rationale": "Eleven production-representative non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs were assembled from the same manufacturing lot and distributed across two independent testing laboratories (Lab A: n=6; Lab B: n=5). Sample-to-sample dimensional variability was characterized by CMM inspection of all 11 screws; coefficient of variation on outer diameter was 0.4%. Inter-laboratory variability was quantified and incorporated into the combined experimental uncertainty estimate."
    },
    {
