        "name": "Test conditions acceptance criteria",
        "description": "ASTM F1717 standard test configuration at a single load level (static monotonic ramp to 40 mm). Achieved Gradation 2: test conditions documented and traceable to standard; single test condition only, not multiple."
      },
      "rationale": "Testing was conducted strictly per ASTM F1717-15 at a single static monotonic load condition. Only one test condition (compression-bending to 40 mm at 5 mm/min crosshead speed) was employed; no variation in load rate, temperature, or pre-load was included. This limits the factor to Gradation 2 rather than the required Gradation 3. An offset rationale is provided in the decision record referencing the strong QoI agreement (all E/uval < 1.4) and the conservative nature of the single-condition comparison."
